> Ohio Janet Jackson, Chicago, The Cars nominated for rock hall FILE - In this Aug. 7, 2011, file photo, lead singer Ric Ocasek of the Cars, performs during the Lollapalooza music festival at Grant Park in Chicago. The band is being considered for induction next year in the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame. (AP Photo/Nam Y. Huh, File) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
